<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/26055420">1994 年版《三国演义》剧中饰演最传神的角色是哪些？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2604998" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">突然对这个很感兴趣。相信大家的讨论会很有意思</div>


</div>
