<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$michael-97-69" href="/people/michael-97-69">Michael</a>，<strong title="愿为曹公一爪牙，终身追随郭祭酒" class="zu-question-my-bio">愿为曹公一爪牙，终身追随郭祭酒</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="725">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-wei-47-73" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-wei-47-73" class="zg-link" title="陈纬">陈纬</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$mu-ai-fei-wei" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/mu-ai-fei-wei" class="zg-link" title="楠小坑">楠小坑</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhou-tong-52" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhou-tong-52" class="zg-link" title="周桐">周桐</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2604998" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">这个必须得是鲍国安老师的曹操啊。<br><br><br><br>祭袁绍时魏武挥鞭、荡平宇内的豪迈气魄。<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/d672ae0c165faa88cac2a97c1e5dc45a_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/d672ae0c165faa88cac2a97c1e5dc45a_r.jpg"><br><br>横槊赋诗，天下归心。登上人生巅峰的曹老板。<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/31c29d14287557f6111e68b744d3a9dd_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/31c29d14287557f6111e68b744d3a9dd_r.jpg"><br><br><br>曾经的热血青年曹孟德<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/faa3650d0d3109b1e3f3cadcf2b28df6_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/faa3650d0d3109b1e3f3cadcf2b28df6_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/880176be9fafe8ada46249cd635149fd_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/880176be9fafe8ada46249cd635149fd_r.jpg"><br><br>数天下英雄时的自信。<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/b99adb9ce03e92932a625247f1da96f7_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/b99adb9ce03e92932a625247f1da96f7_r.jpg"><br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/11cd2780b01e1193e494a56246b37316_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/11cd2780b01e1193e494a56246b37316_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/f7df5e4321ec328ad2a650d716be59c1_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/f7df5e4321ec328ad2a650d716be59c1_r.jpg"><br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/ffec35d10fa97fb8ddaee7c0af0f7575_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/ffec35d10fa97fb8ddaee7c0af0f7575_r.jpg"><br><br><br>谁说曹公只爱云长，看看人家看奉孝这眼神<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/66384463f09afd8c58abbf03816485b1_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/66384463f09afd8c58abbf03816485b1_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/7a541cbf913111c8bafcd4df1fc8269f_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/7a541cbf913111c8bafcd4df1fc8269f_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/34aa2b58d061c46b39cdfcda4fce6d01_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/34aa2b58d061c46b39cdfcda4fce6d01_r.jpg"><br><br><br><br>观沧海，思奉孝<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/766c5aff7ef2b54e155f5ec9483c6f16_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/766c5aff7ef2b54e155f5ec9483c6f16_r.jpg"><br><br>怎么能没有这一幕呢？<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/001373e635f54cfa91877d864d94107c_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/001373e635f54cfa91877d864d94107c_r.jpg"><br><br><br>一些小的动作细节也特别到位：<br>陈琳檄文治头痛，曹老板卖萌<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/90898a91c6e81fb425aa6e1b538fc06d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/90898a91c6e81fb425aa6e1b538fc06d_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/4f15c92ef783510cd7c8531a139db85c_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/4f15c92ef783510cd7c8531a139db85c_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/bcc616a23f4f7c7c0cd676fd409328fc_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/bcc616a23f4f7c7c0cd676fd409328fc_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/e2341a0825c53dcc4895bc3447547887_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/e2341a0825c53dcc4895bc3447547887_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/62ebef5770a489095d7a6e282f153d09_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/62ebef5770a489095d7a6e282f153d09_r.jpg"><br><br>待我捋捋胡子装个逼，哦，忘了刚刚才割须弃袍……<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/b9344be10956f04fadfbe52cb9b4dc84_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/b9344be10956f04fadfbe52cb9b4dc84_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/ad26cab0824de654813230d539a4775d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/ad26cab0824de654813230d539a4775d_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/09e18174d4254be2c234c4700a1e9884_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/09e18174d4254be2c234c4700a1e9884_r.jpg"><br><br><br><br><br>错杀蔡张，汉末好颜艺。<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/c6ed3473efc9688ba988adca03ad32a1_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/c6ed3473efc9688ba988adca03ad32a1_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/41ccf6c131f6afbd5ae29220ea98cc47_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/41ccf6c131f6afbd5ae29220ea98cc47_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/53e76e93b6d981d997de30a80826f801_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/53e76e93b6d981d997de30a80826f801_r.jpg"><br><br><br>述志令<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/a1bd5a36df60f5bfedb995f2b4582ad0_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/a1bd5a36df60f5bfedb995f2b4582ad0_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/5bb5689d1f1f3afc1fd90b3ec0b4f8e4_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/5bb5689d1f1f3afc1fd90b3ec0b4f8e4_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/f45a531940563c6523bf3f56970d1da6_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/f45a531940563c6523bf3f56970d1da6_r.jpg"><br><br><br><br>恍然大悟表情包：<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e9543d674cd1f5e7f28f5d563785549e_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/e9543d674cd1f5e7f28f5d563785549e_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/1a99e6cb241554f3341255c66b55d0ad_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/1a99e6cb241554f3341255c66b55d0ad_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/c2979bf476b3feee8bccfba74f31abef_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/c2979bf476b3feee8bccfba74f31abef_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/312a79ca5496b772952b48a653f0af9a_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/312a79ca5496b772952b48a653f0af9a_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/34405dbcb04eba6a71cd332ad954285d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/34405dbcb04eba6a71cd332ad954285d_r.jpg"><br><br><br><br>赤壁兵败，曹老板笑一次来一次伏兵，最后一次演得尤其妙：<br>先是第三次大笑：<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/1176646ac902d99f3247280e83d2fc01_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/1176646ac902d99f3247280e83d2fc01_r.jpg"><br><br>忽然发现好像有什么不对，<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/866646e77240a1548f04c9d97159eed8_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/866646e77240a1548f04c9d97159eed8_r.jpg"><br><br>看了看路口，确实没人。<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/db4be7ae0581258b9350face746dec57_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/db4be7ae0581258b9350face746dec57_r.jpg"><br>于是继续大笑，话说你能不能考虑一下您身后浪里白条张辽的感受啊！看看人家都被你吓成个啥了。<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/82379090123471cc2c4816728d0a0418_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/82379090123471cc2c4816728d0a0418_r.jpg"><br><br>于是……<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/b29ad10d16a33b3515098199930a9a34_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/b29ad10d16a33b3515098199930a9a34_r.jpg"><br><br>因为…<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/594b773bf45bc66ba0d9ccfc84a8ef03_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/594b773bf45bc66ba0d9ccfc84a8ef03_r.jpg"><br><br><br><br>最后再来一个“云长去矣五连拍”，曹老板委屈死了。<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/557ab0a16e9d5374b74aa3b0b84b93fa_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/557ab0a16e9d5374b74aa3b0b84b93fa_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/1832c9d83162d8601717c037a4edbcb9_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/1832c9d83162d8601717c037a4edbcb9_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/c66c848dce75bf6d028157ff15beb3ef_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/c66c848dce75bf6d028157ff15beb3ef_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/319a327b9bc2b004defe004eef86d3c7_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/319a327b9bc2b004defe004eef86d3c7_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/d13f3f997fec2c5fb70b8a83b9c0b8b8_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/d13f3f997fec2c5fb70b8a83b9c0b8b8_r.jpg"><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>彩蛋：曹老板教你来约炮<br><br>第一步：你要有一个忠（la）心（pi）护（tiao）卫（de）<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/31c83f891536b3f640c77eccb7b1739a_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/31c83f891536b3f640c77eccb7b1739a_r.jpg"><br><br>第二步：展示自己的权势和威名<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/10b736095f4fdf912abdfcbfbe42c89d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/10b736095f4fdf912abdfcbfbe42c89d_r.jpg"><br><br><br>第三步：让对方觉得自己很重要，顺便继续炫耀权势。<img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/799dd2e1794e8dbac978c1c14c8be840_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/799dd2e1794e8dbac978c1c14c8be840_r.jpg"><br><br><br>第四步：约否？<img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/472c861e50fe2971a6a2c73d8e99c28b_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/472c861e50fe2971a6a2c73d8e99c28b_r.jpg"><br><br><br>第五步：搞定<br><img data-rawheight="1536" data-rawwidth="2048" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/bf49c2cb425adcf7a4276485733bbe1d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/bf49c2cb425adcf7a4276485733bbe1d_r.jpg">
