</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2604998" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">一定要回答这个问题，因为太喜欢鲍老师的曹操了。<img data-rawheight="572" data-rawwidth="750" src="//pic2.zhimg.com/6a4616440fbf5e27a126a9bf19e1b851_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="750" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/6a4616440fbf5e27a126a9bf19e1b851_r.jpg"><br><img data-rawheight="640" data-rawwidth="800" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/5a218763fc4c490315ca8de79c921a28_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/5a218763fc4c490315ca8de79c921a28_r.jpg">鲍老师把曹操的诡谲，阴狠，霸气，自信，坦率都表现得淋漓尽致。<br>曹老板有时候也很温柔阿。比如说郭嘉死的这一段，<img data-rawheight="767" data-rawwidth="1025" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/45af50beed7ff12cce30e75c547c3798_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1025" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/45af50beed7ff12cce30e75c547c3798_r.jpg">这里曹操与郭嘉离别时的一声带着哭腔的嗯简直催人断肠阿。<img data-rawheight="768" data-rawwidth="1025" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/cb7a8209b3b9ec835f7f61a000aa5ab7_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1025" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/cb7a8209b3b9ec835f7f61a000aa5ab7_r.jpg">眼神很温柔有木有。<br><br>还有是曹操迎许攸，那一段简直神演技！！<img data-rawheight="768" data-rawwidth="1024" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/8117d4486335f740eb04e74669c5c13a_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/8117d4486335f740eb04e74669c5c13a_r.jpg"><img data-rawheight="768" data-rawwidth="1023" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/4fcce4661e64e2e49ff2b4b22c8611c4_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1023" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/4fcce4661e64e2e49ff2b4b22c8611c4_r.jpg">超级超级萌的！！！<br><br><br><br><br>还有诸位说的陈琳檄文，观沧海，割须弃袍等等。<img data-rawheight="439" data-rawwidth="584" src="//pic3.zhimg.com/d430c74ba8e4ce1860c3f347f2c462fa_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="584" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/d430c74ba8e4ce1860c3f347f2c462fa_r.jpg"><br><br>最后附上几张萌图<img data-rawheight="768" data-rawwidth="1366" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/3eec749c4a2282a95c30665777c72423_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1366" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/3eec749c4a2282a95c30665777c72423_r.jpg"><br><br><img data-rawheight="640" data-rawwidth="1136" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/953bb4ba4f91bab7f5a622215ec645c0_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1136" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/953bb4ba4f91bab7f5a622215ec645c0_r.jpg"><br><br><img data-rawheight="640" data-rawwidth="1136" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/2dfc5cef23ad0ed31b8db9e79fed1aab_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1136" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/2dfc5cef23ad0ed31b8db9e79fed1aab_r.jpg"><br><br>嗯，就这样。
<a href="/question/26055420/answer/33886725" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
